 
'''Dean Kamen''' - famous for the invention of the [[Segway]]{{w|Segway}}, the two-wheeled [[transport]] using a gyroscope for balance - has also developed: 
* The [[Slingshot water purifier]]
* [[Kamen's Stirling engine]]
* The [[iBOT]]{{w|iBOT}} [[wheelchair]] based on the technology used in the Segway.

